SAML configuration (using Spring Security as per SAK-30105):

federationmetadata.xml is supplied by the ADFS SAML server: https://adfs.uct.ac.za/federationmetadata/2007-06/federationmetadata.xml

SP metadata is generated automatically by Spring Security, at the URL /sakai-login-tool/container/saml/metadata

The metadata files here are for reference only.
